{"tid":1833153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉事海關船隻為中國製造","createTime":"2020-01-21T16:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T16:46:53.000Z","uid":209657,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da36d5c4c29a80810134084abcb6614bce7f5f82","tid":1833153,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"據了解，涉事船隻為海關船隻，屬淺水巡邏艇，為中國製造。事發時正在執行追截任務。"},{"pid":"09bc2cb0e9458349656bcbdb6356ddf79f3abeb3","tid":1833153,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"晚上9時許，警方接報指，屯門龍鼓灘對出沙洲海面，一艘船撞及不明物體沉沒，船上5人墮海。水警到場救起最少兩人，搜救仍在進行中。最新消息指，5人已全部獲救，其中兩男清醒送北大嶼山醫院，另2男1女昏迷，送往屯門醫院。"},{"pid":"2ccd4444ef550c87daeb0a72667d7ab95512d2a5","tid":1833153,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"【海關殉職】海關沙洲快艇沉沒　三名海關人員送院後不治"},{"pid":"fe2ba7cc4fa3edfe6bbca59313c5e83fd38f3241","tid":1833153,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:25:13.000Z","msg":"子華套戲都係深圳製造啦 又唔見佢沉船？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d580efdad4e7417bce2a7d9d80244b4f470e0a6a","tid":1833153,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"資料顯示，該艘淺水巡邏艇由內地製造，於2016年投入服務，負責淺水巡邏、追截高速船隻及配合潛水隊工作。該艇最高航速達50海里，以每個350匹的雙引擎推動。"},{"pid":"51e1fc446973b7c4fe9fe6485ea16e1c115640fe","tid":1833153,"uid":133383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"中國製造！天有眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8344dc987a58bf8e3d39954ca704e67846799f","tid":1833153,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"明白了"}]}